title: Hard.Drive.LED.v.1.103.WINDOWS.DeadLights
description:
HddLed Indicator is a tool to monitor hard drive activity. If your PC is out of sight or even has no HDD LED on the PC box, HddLed Indicator will help to monitor hard drive activity. 

With HddLed Indicator you can select which of the logical disks or hard drives you want to look after. And dynamic tips will get more information about rate and amount of transferred data.
